President Donald J. Trump and First Lady Melania Trump issued a statement on April 17, 2018, celebrating the life of Barbara Bush. They acknowledged her role as a wife, mother, grandmother, military spouse, and former First Lady, and highlighted her advocacy for the American family. One of her greatest achievements was promoting literacy as a fundamental family value. The President and First Lady expressed their condolences to the Bush family and friends, and recognized Barbara Bush's unwavering devotion to both country and family.